1. *Pogotovo* onda kada se odlučujemo da uradimo nešto novo. (Especially then when we decide to do something new.)
2. Uvek se trudim da se pridržavam svojih principa, *pogotovo* kada je u pitanju obaveza prema drugima. (I always try to adhere to my principles, especially when it comes to obligations to others.)
3. Njegov posao je postao veoma zahtevan, *pogotovo* nakon što je preuzeo više odgovornosti. (His job has become very demanding, especially after he took on more responsibility.)
4. On je veoma disciplinovan čovek, *pogotovo* kada je u pitanju njegov rad. (He is a very disciplined man, especially when it comes to his work.)
5. Ona je veoma uspešna u školi, *pogotovo* u matematici. (She is very successful in school, especially in mathematics.)